Package: SeuratExtra
Title: Professional Visualization Extensions for Seurat
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Shiyue", "Zhang", , "shiyue_z@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of plotting utilities for Seurat objects, 
    designed for high-impact journal publications. Includes optimized 
    dimension reduction plots with customized corner-arrow axes, 
    automatic legend balancing, and rasterization support for large-scale 
    single-cell datasets.
